1. *Zvoni* telefon. (The phone is ringing.)
2. Telefon *zvoni*. (The phone is ringing.)
3. *Zvonio* je telefon ceo dan. (The phone rang all day.)
4. Čula sam kako *zvoni* telefon. (I heard the phone ringing.)
5. Kada sam ušao u kuću, *zvonio* je telefon. (When I entered the house, the phone was ringing.)
6. Molim te da *zvoniš* ako kasniš. (Please call if you're late.)
7. Svakog jutra *zvoni* budilnik u 7. (The alarm clock rings every morning at 7.)
8. Šta se desi ako *zvoni* alarm? (What happens if the alarm rings?)
9. Pitao sam je da li će *zvoniti* na vratima kada stigne. (I asked her if she will ring the doorbell when she arrives.)
10. Kada *zvoni* crkveno zvono, znači da je vreme za molitvu. (When the church bell rings, it means it's time for prayer.)